== Availability ==
Pretty much any Teladi shipyard will sell the Kestrel.

The Kestrel Advanced and Pirate Kestrel are not available for purchase.

{| style="text-align:center;"
|- style="{{Colour/Teladi}}"
! width="120px" | Variant !! [[Ceo's Sprite]] !! [[Grand Exchange]] !! [[Ianamus Zura]] !! [[Ministry of Finance]] !! [[PTNI Headquarters]] !! [[Seizewell]]
|-
! style="text-align:left;" | Kestrel ||   || x || x  || x || x || x
|}

== Suggested Roles==

Perfectly capable of mapping, scouting, ferrying passengers and any task where running away quickly is useful.

This craft is the best ship for doing the [[Follow Ship]] missions because the target you're required to follow will sometimes fly an [[M5]] vessel.

This craft can support JumpDrive permit short jump, is excellent for speed mission.

